Coach, Xu Fang wasn't like this before.

54
00:04:33,370 --> 00:04:35,690
Something's wrong with him—

55
00:04:35,699 --> 00:04:37,679
Xu Fang, you can do it!

56
00:04:39,980 --> 00:04:44,659
Will you be seeing Ding Yi again in this competition?
- Congratulations.

57
00:04:44,659 --> 00:04:48,020
Xu Fang, you're my most favorite player.

58
00:04:48,020 --> 00:04:50,618
He wants me to make a great player out of you.

59
00:04:50,618 --> 00:04:53,740
Among all of your arrows,

60
